    <h3>What This Might Look Like</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>A quiet sense that you're not alone</li>
      <li>The ability to breathe again without explanation</li>
      <li>Permission to rest — without doing more first</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h3>What This Might Need</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Stillness, space, or a memory of being held</li>
      <li>Repetition of a phrase like “She’s here.” or “She still exists.”</li>
      <li>No interruptions, no fixing — just quiet fidelity</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

